com.sri.ai.grinder.core

Class DefaultRegistry

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sri.ai.grinder.core.DefaultRegistry
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Registry, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable

    @Beta
public class DefaultRegistry
extends java.lang.Object
implements Registry, java.io.Serializable
    A default implementation of Registry.

    By default, the predicate indicating variables uses PrologVariableConvention.

    Author:
    braz, oreilly
